{"tid":1785784,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有邊間做燒鼻息肉手術係平靚正","createTime":"2019-12-16T15:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T04:04:51.000Z","uid":35857,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"759350a26e253bad16c0314206025d6ab25bb978","tid":1785784,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"個鼻塞咗好多年了<br />\n想做手術<br />\n去睇公立醫院 又話我唔嚴重唔撚畀我轉介<br />\n明明塞到呼吸都辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲有介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd269e89f12af9efabfd9973ef4a7aa8c678697","tid":1785784,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1417f5f640623afb82ed192733e6cf2287a515f6","tid":1785784,"uid":70485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df223c66dbc75dc41210892ecd821ee57fc2958d","tid":1785784,"uid":35484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:48:05.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7syZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=edd73cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7syZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=6234ffe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"54d4e693cdb8f1755f91d57256cf992d656d4af9","tid":1785784,"uid":251549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:51:16.000Z","msg":"我都應該有類似問題<br />\n啱先開始排公家 要等2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓覺果時最塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d13afb5da68d150ca752f57ce557ef6fe3a4a7","tid":1785784,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T19:02:56.000Z","msg":"聽講做完會生返出嚟再塞過？<br />\n塞咗一世人，好辛苦"},{"pid":"48443b19dad69684766a19b35b5735c4a66d2721","tid":1785784,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:04:59.000Z","msg":"以前做左切割<br />\n感覺又發炎生翻一半出嚟"},{"pid":"bd431890263e563f4069e67b9a34d7b933edf2da","tid":1785784,"uid":85822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"本身想切 以前食3隻敏感藥先透到氣<br />\n<br />\n不過改變左飲食習慣 同埋飲左隻抗敏茶就好左好多<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油"},{"pid":"c8b19981a6db421873a7505598764c35e9237f91","tid":1785784,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd431890263e563f4069e67b9a34d7b933edf2da","tid":1785784,"uid":85822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"本身想切 以前食3隻敏感藥先透到氣<br />\n<br />\n不過改變左飲食習慣 同埋飲左隻抗敏茶就好左好多<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:52:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講改變咗咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047f12bd04919eba4815c7730f271914e5facaa7","tid":1785784,"uid":85822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c8b19981a6db421873a7505598764c35e9237f91","tid":1785784,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd431890263e56